skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: who am i
des:
To play "Who I am?" Alexa needs to know your age to set the difficulty of the riddles accordingly.
Then, Alexa will pretend to be someone and tell you something about herself. You try to guess who she is or can get another hint. This goes on until you have discovered who she is.

Currently, the following age groups are distinguished:
- 0-10 years (animals and objects)
- 11-19 years (characters and celebrities)
- 20 years and older (historical characters and celebrities)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
